In [12]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(2, 2)
ax1, ax2, ax3, ax4 = ax.flatten()

ax1.plot(x, y1)
ax1.set_title(' y1')
ax1.set_xlim(-5, 5)

ax2.plot(x, y2)
ax2.set_title(' y2')

ax3.plot(x, y3)
ax3.set_title(' y3')

ax4.plot(x, y4)
ax4.set_title(' y4')

fig.set_size_inches(8, 6)
plt.subplots_adjust(wspace=0.3, hspace=0.3)
